        <descript>
            <abstract>Statewide dataset containing the location of state, local and selected private roads and their associated attributes, including road names. For attribute data dictionary, see the file RDIUserGuide.pdf.</abstract>
            <purpose>The data may be used to map the statewide road network, and/or to query for physical and administrative features of individual road segments.</purpose>
            <supplinf>Data distribution tile: statewide NH Public Roads represents the most frequently distributed dataset. Additional transportation-related datasets may be available directly from NHDOT.</supplinf>
        </descript>
